      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how tiny everything is. like, the universe is just expanding into nothingness and in a few billion years there wont be a single trace that we ever even existed. it makes everything i do feel so pointless. why even bother trying to build anything or be anything if it's all just gonna be erased anyway?",
